    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 72-77.</p><p>Arcanism of the Outer Planes</p><p>Starting when you reach 24th level, your Patron gifts you with a powerful arcanism that you can manifest into the world, a spell that best represents its energy and power. Depending on your Patron, you can cast one of the following 9th-level spells by expending 2 Legendary Points. Once you cast this spell, you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest. If you are playing a subclass other than the ones listed below, work with your DM to choose a 9th-level spell that best represents your Patron. Alternatively, choose one of the following.</p></div>",
